 book. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003ca href=\"http://yoursmiles.org/t-heart.php?page=3\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\n  \u003cimg src=\"https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1418251830ra/12721004.gif\" class=\"gr-hostedUserImg\" loading=\"lazy\"\u003e\n\u003c/a\u003e \u003ci\u003eShort and sweet:\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cb\u003eI feel like most readers: 'Magical reading!!'\u003c/b\u003e. \u003cbr\u003eThis writer is a stunning master writer of this HR genre. Do you plan to only read one single historical m/f romance in the coming year: Please, select one written by Judith McNaught, you can not but be happy and satisfied. — Grand and great, and so neat and well told. I loved it all. There will be more JMN romances in my \"\u003cu\u003eRead\u003c/u\u003e\" shelf. Many many more hopefully.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cb\u003eI LIKE - OF COURSE, who doesn't?\u003c/b\u003e ","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/15589375?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"romance-m-f-historical","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/15589375?shelf=romance-m-f-historical"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/962642417"},"likeCount":37,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":30,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:12125670":{"id":12125670,"__typename":"User","legacyId":12125670,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1417537732i/12125670._UX200_CR0,58,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":905,"viewableName":"♥Sharon♥","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/12125670-sharon","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":144},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.LxrxApB05JuRmu14t6XPpg":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr